<sect1 id="dir_3dba072b2489bebe845ad485d4f2a8c5_1autotoc_md385">
<title>helios::engine::runtime::spawn::behavior</title><para>Spawn behavior strategies for positioning and initializing entities.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_3dba072b2489bebe845ad485d4f2a8c5_1autotoc_md386">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides the behavior layer for the spawn system. It defines abstract interfaces and concrete implementations for determining where entities spawn and how they are initialized.</para>
</sect1>
